[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m Let $x,y$ and $z$ be positive real numbers that satisfy the following system of equations: 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m \[\log_2\left({x \over yz}\right) = {1 \over 2}\]
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m \[\log_2\left({y \over xz}\right) = {1 \over 3}\]
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m \[\log_2\left({z \over xy}\right) = {1 \over 4}\]
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m Then the value of $\left|\log_2(x^4y^3z^2)\right|$ is $\tfrac{m}{n}$ where $m$ and $n$ are relatively prime positive integers. Find $m+n$.
