[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m \[ a + b + c = -\frac{13}{12} \]
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m Now we can find \(a\), \(b\), and \(c\) individually:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m \[ a = (a + b + c) - (b + c) = -\frac{13}{12} - \left(-\frac{19}{24}\right) = -\frac{13}{12} + \frac{19}{24} = -\frac{26}{24} + \frac{19}{24} = -\frac{7}{24} \]
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m \[ b = (a + b + c) - (a + c) = -\frac{13}{12} - \left(-\frac{17}{24}\right) = -\frac{13}{12} + \frac{17}{24} = -\frac{26}{24} + \frac{17}{24} = -\frac{9}{24} = -\frac{3}{8} \]
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3370463)[0m \[ c = (a + b + c) - (a + b) = -\frac{13}{12} - \left(-\frac{2}{3}\right) = -\frac{13}{12} + \frac{8}{12} = -\frac{5}{12} \]
